Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_disable_timing(25.10)                        reset_disable_timing(25.10)

Name
       reset_disable_timing  -  Restores  timing arcs that were disabled using
       the set_disable_timing command

Syntax
       reset_disable_timing

       [-help]

       [-from <pin_name> -to <pin_name>]

       <object_list>

       Restores timing arcs that were disabled  using  the  set_disable_timing
       command.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -from <pin_name> -to <pin_name>
              Specifies  the arc(s) that are to be restored. Specify the -from
              and -to options together.

              You can specify the -from  and  -to  parameters  when  the  <ob-
              ject_list>  contains  instance  or  library cell objects. Do not
              specify the -from and -to parameters when the <object_list>  in-
              cludes instance pin or library cell pin objects.

              The  -from  and  -to options are optional. If not specified, all
              cell arcs found in the instance or library cell objects are  re-
              stored.

       <object_list>
              Specifies the instance, instance pin, library arc, library cell,
              or library cell pin objects.

              If  the  <object_list> includes instance pin or library cell pin
              objects, all cell arcs attached to the specified pin objects are
              restored.

              If the <object_list> contains instance or library cell  objects,
              and  the  -from  and  -to parameters are not specified, all arcs
              found in the specified instance or library cell objects are  re-
              stored.

Examples
              * The  following commands set and reset the timing arcs and dis-
                play the resulting reports:

                set_disable_timing -from A -to Y [get_cells b1]

                report_inactive_arcs

                ---------------------------------------------------------------

                Flags :              const                 propagated constant

                                     snipped               loop snipped arcs

                                     disable               set_disable_timing

                                     disable_clock_gating             set_dis-
                able_clock_gating

                                     library_disable                  set_dis-
                able_cell_timing

                                     Missing_Phase         No Arc Phase Data

                From       To       DisableType  ArcType         Reason

                -------------------------------------------------------------

                b1/A ^     b1/Y ^   disable      combinational   User Disable

                b1/A v     b1/Y v   disable      combinational   User Disable

                -------------------------------------------------------------

              * The following commands disable the timing report header:

                set_global timing_disable_report_header_info true

                report_inactive_arcs

                ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

                Flags :                   const                     propagated
                constant

                                          snipped                         loop
                snipped arcs

                                          disable                     set_dis-
                able_timing

                                          disable_clock_gating        set_dis-
                able_clock_gating

                                          library_disable             set_dis-
                able_cell_timing

                                          Missing_Phase               No   Arc
                Phase Data

                From              To              DisableType          ArcType
                Reason

                ----------------------------------------------------------------------

                u8/CK  ^     u8/D  ^     const            hold_rising_clk_rise
                u8/D = 1

                u8/CK  ^     u8/D  v     const           hold_falling_clk_rise
                u8/D = 1

                u8/CK  ^     u8/D  ^     const           setup_rising_clk_rise
                u8/D = 1

                u8/CK  ^     u8/D  v     const          setup_falling_clk_rise
                u8/D = 1

                ---------------------------------------------------------------------

              * The following commands disable the timing arcs from  CK  to  Q
                for  instance U8, then reset the assertions using the instance
                reference:

                set_disable_timing -from CK -to Q [get_cells u8]

                report_inactive_arcs

                -----------------------------------------------------------------

                Flags :                const                  propagated  con-
                stant

                                       snipped               loop snipped arcs

                                       disable                set_disable_tim-
                ing

                                       disable_clock_gating           set_dis-
                able_clock_gating

                                       library_disable                set_dis-
                able_cell_timing

                                       Missing_Phase         No Arc Phase Data

                From       To       DisableType     ArcType       Reason

                -----------------------------------------------------------------

                u8/CK ^    u8/Q ^   disable         rising_edge   User Disable

                u8/CK ^    u8/Q v   disable         rising_edge   User Disable

                ----------------------------------------------------------------

              * The following commands disable the timing arcs from  CK  to  Q
                for  instance U8, then reset the assertions using the instance
                reference:

                reset_disable_timing u8

                report_inactive_arcs

                -------------------------------------------------------------------------

                Flags  :                    const                   propagated
                constant

                                          snipped                loop  snipped
                arcs

                                          disable                     set_dis-
                able_timing

                                          disable_clock_gating        set_dis-
                able_clock_gating

                                          library_disable             set_dis-
                able_cell_timing

                                          Missing_Phase          No  Arc Phase
                Data

                From            To              DisableType            ArcType
                Reason

                --------------------------------------------------------------------------

                u8/CK   ^     u8/D  ^    const            hold_rising_clk_rise
                u8/D = 1

                u8/CK  ^    u8/D  v    const             hold_falling_clk_rise
                u8/D = 1

                u8/CK   ^    u8/D  ^    const            setup_rising_clk_rise
                u8/D = 1

                u8/CK  ^    u8/D  v    const            setup_falling_clk_rise
                u8/D = 1

                --------------------------------------------------------------------------

